# Kikman Enterprises

> Parent holding company for ventures founded by Travis Neuman and Trenton Kik. The central entity that owns, manages, and provides strategic direction to portfolio companies.

---

## Overview

**Kikman Enterprises** serves as the umbrella organization for various entrepreneurial ventures. The name combines the founders' surnames: **Kik**man from Trenton Kik and Neu**man** from Travis Neuman.

### Why a Holding Company?

A holding company structure provides several key benefits ([Source](https://www.delawareinc.com/blog/how-to-operate-multiple-businesses-under-one-llc/)):

| Benefit | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| **Liability Protection** | Each subsidiary's debts and liabilities are isolated, protecting other ventures and personal assets |
| **Tax Efficiency** | Consolidated tax planning, potential pass-through benefits, and strategic loss allocation |
| **Asset Protection** | Assets held by the holding company are shielded from liability arising in operating entities |
| **Centralized Management** | Financial, legal, and strategic decisions made at holding level |
| **Investor Ready** | Well-understood structure by banks and investors |

